<br>
They did not nerf the damage itself. The massive amount of damage stays the same. Turning regular crits into massive damage on undead mobs.<br>
<br>
They changed it from a passive ability(always on), to an activated one with No refresh time. So technically you can still have it on at all times. <br>
<br>
BUT they added a drawback. You get hit for more damage than usual from undead mobs when you use this. <br>
<br>
Pretty much similar to the way our lvl 60 Aggressive discipline works. We hit for more damage(small amount) during 3 minutes, refresh time is 27 minutes. Cannot use any other disciplines until the refresh timer expires. <br>
<br>
