Kinda like when rogues backstab and after they score big damage and steal aggro they Evade and turn attack off.<br>
<br>
This is still a powerful situational damage dealing ability. Probably the reason it got nerfed is because PoP will offer a lot more Undead mobs or a whole Zone of them.<br>
<br>
This will indeed affect drastically the paladin that soloed undead mobs for exp. But not the paladin in a group/raid where he is not the MT and just another damage dealer. <br>
<br>
At least thats what  I viewed from this post from Absor. Did I misread something? <br>
